getFriend 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Returns if sides are friendly or hostile. For a value smaller than 
 0.6 it results in being enemy, otherwise it's friendly.   
Syntax:  
 side1 getFriend side2 
Parameters: 
side1: Side 
side2: Side 
Return Value: 
 Number: Decimal value between 0.0 to 1.0